item.title: Scania R&S New Bumper, Front Fender, Interior v1.0 ETS2
item.description:
Scania R&S New Bumper, Front Fender, Interior v1.0 ETS2

This mod adds innovations for the R and S cabins of the scania pgrs mod belonging to eugene.

New Added:
– New 40mm Bumper (Model: SCS Software)
– New Front Fender (Model: SCS Software)
– New Interior (Model: SCS Software)
– Ownable Scania S&R BEV Electric
– Scania PGRS Pack 1.50.



How to install ETS2 mods or ATS Mods

In Euro Truck Simulator 2 it’s easy to install mods. You just need to download mod from here, copy/unzip files into: “My Documents\Euro Truck Simulator 2\mod” folder or if you play ATS please install mods to: “My Documents\American Truck Simulator\mod” folder. To unzip files you can use: WinRAR or 7zip. After that you need to activate the mods you want to use.

item.title: KamAZ Pack 5460 / 6460 / 65117 / 65201 / 4326 / 65221 / 43118 / 65228 1.50.x ETS2
item.description:
KamAZ Pack 5460 / 6460 / 65117 / 65201 / 4326 / 65221 / 43118 / 65228 1.50.x ETS2

Autonomous, does not replace anything, is bought at KamAZ modification dealers
KamAZ 5460 has 4 chassis and one “C3” cabin, generation K2
KamAZ 4326 has 4 chassis and one “C3” cabin, generation K2
This KAMAZ has real technical characteristics (dimensions, weight, etc.) – technical data are taken from the official website the KamAZ-Center Belarus website
All engines, gearboxes and gear ratios are prescribed for certain chassis – technical data are adjusted to the data of real trucks
Your own salon
Have a “walking” camera on the passenger seat
Support for interior lighting (dumis “light”, 7 options to choose from). The light turns on when power is applied to the dimensions (letter K)
Has its own KamAZ and Cummins sounds
3 modes of operation of windscreen wipers
A large selection of tuning
Supports steering wheel adjustment
Supports “Advanced trailer coupling” on all chassis
Have “Trailer cables” on all chassis
Supports adjustable chassis suspension
Have animation of windows and handles

The game version is 1.50, it is possible to work on 1.49 (I have not personally tested it)

item.title: BDF Trailers NEFAZ 8332-01/04 for KAMAZ 8×1 1.50.x ETS2
item.description:
BDF Trailers NEFAZ 8332-01/04 for KAMAZ 8×1 1.50.x ETS2

Trailers pack NEFAZ 8332-01/04 for KAMAZ 8×1 (highway and off-road versions under chassis 65117 and 65221)
They are bought into the property
Each body has its own registered cargos
12 body options
These trailers have real technical characteristics (dimensions, weight, etc.) – technical data taken from the official website of NEFAZ
Supports “Advanced trailer coupling”
Have “Trailer cables”
There is no tuning

My changes:
Updated all 3D models to version 1.50
The registration of cargo, trailers, etc. has been completely rewritten[normal] The registration of chassis, dimensions, and weight for real TTX trailers has been completely rewritten
All names of cargo, types of trailers, etc. have been translated into Russian, Ukrainian, and English!
Unnecessary files were found and deleted, due to this, the weight of the mod is slightly reduced
Double trailers have been removed (due to the irrationality of using them in the game)
Missing .mat files have been added and all errors in the log have been removed!

The game version is 1.50, it is possible to work on 1.49 (I have not personally tested it)
